					<div class="markdown">




					<h3>HTML代码</h3>
						<pre><code class="html">
&lt;!--默认--&gt;
&lt;input id=&quot;picker1&quot; class=&quot;form-control form-control-inline input-medium date-picker&quot; size=&quot;16&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; value=&quot;&quot;/&gt;


